#!/bin/sh

PROMPT="
Collect data that I request, below, and combine it into a morning brief.

Print the brief to standard out using simple html -- paragraphs, lists, bold and italic fonts, headings. 
Respond with raw HTML only. No markdown, no code fences, no explanation. Just the HTML document starting with <!DOCTYPE html>.

Do not narrate or explain what you are doing. Output only the HTML, nothing else.

Requested data:
- top 5 articles from https://www.canarymedia.com/, one summary, of 15 words or less, per article.
claude

If you encounter problems, try web search or other work arounds.

If you report both content from articles and information on your own activites, put the content first and the information on your activities at the very end.

This is an automated script and you should not ask questions because I will not be able to answer them.
"

claude --allowedTools WebFetch,WebSearch -p "$PROMPT"
